== Overview ==

Dragon Quest I & II features the heroes of both games. DQ1 has a single hero while DQ2 features a party of three descendants.

== Character Data Structure ==

Character data is 32 bytes per character:

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Offset !! Size !! Description
|-
| $00 || 8 || Name (4 characters + padding)
|-
| $08-$09 || 2 || Current HP
|-
| $0A-$0B || 2 || Max HP
|-
| $0C-$0D || 2 || Current MP
|-
| $0E-$0F || 2 || Max MP
|-
| $10 || 1 || Strength
|-
| $11 || 1 || Agility
|-
| $12 || 1 || Vitality (SNES only)
|-
| $13 || 1 || Intelligence (SNES only)
|-
| $14 || 1 || Luck (SNES only)
|-
| $15 || 1 || Level
|-
| $16-$19 || 4 || Experience
|-
| $1A-$1D || 4 || Gold
|-
| $1E || 1 || Equipment slots
|-
| $1F || 1 || Status flags
|}

